# .gitignore — Atlanta Sports Hub
# This file tells Git which files NOT to upload to GitHub.
# Currently empty — this is a plain HTML/CSS/JS project
# with nothing to ignore.
#
# Common things you might add later if the project grows:
#
# .DS_Store          ← Mac system file, no need to upload
# Thumbs.db          ← Windows system file
# node_modules/      ← if you ever add npm packages
# .env               ← if you ever add secret keys/passwords
